==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Caller
<hw>Cal"ler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <mark>[Scot.]</mark>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Cool; refreshing; fresh; <as>as, a <ex>caller</ex> day;
the <ex>caller</ex> air</as>.</def> <rj><au>Jamieson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Fresh; in good condition; <as>as, <ex>caller</ex>
berrings</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Callet</ent>⟦br⟧
